{
  "message": "docs: add WebP screenshots for README visual tour\n\nAdd 15 high-quality WebP screenshots converted from PNG originals\nfor the README.md visual tour section. WebP format provides ~77%\nfile size reduction compared to PNG while maintaining visual quality.\n\nScreenshots Included:\n\nHero & Welcome:\n- desktop_full_interface.webp (99KB): Full desktop layout with\n  Lambda phage, 3D structure viewer, and sequence grid\n- hero_welcome_modal.webp (29KB): Interactive welcome tour modal\n\nCore Visualization:\n- lambda_phage_3d_structure.webp (82KB): 3D protein structure viewer\n  with cartoon rendering mode\n- phage_selector_with_preview.webp (46KB): Phage dropdown with\n  genome stats and structure preview\n- main_interface_overview.webp (83KB): Control deck and navigation\n\nAnalysis Tools:\n- analysis_menu_tools.webp (41KB): Analysis menu showing 30+ overlays\n- gc_skew_visualization.webp (81KB): GC skew cumulative plot\n- sequence_complexity_analysis.webp (81KB): Shannon entropy overlay\n\nNavigation & Keyboard:\n- keyboard_shortcuts_help.webp (40KB): Full keyboard shortcuts modal\n- three_dimensional_protein_view.webp (81KB): WebGL 3D viewer\n- sequence_grid_zoomed_detail.webp (81KB): Zoomed nucleotide view\n- sequence_grid_full_genome.webp (82KB): Full genome overview\n\nMobile Experience:\n- mobile_responsive_interface.webp (30KB): Mobile portrait layout\n- mobile_action_drawer.webp (30KB): Bottom sheet action drawer\n- terminal_aesthetic_dark_theme.webp (82KB): Dark terminal theme\n\nTotal: ~967KB (vs ~4.2MB original PNGs)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
